These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-1::.
There 4 different types of food: cherry, lime, zucchini, spinach
1. the person eating cherry is on the far left##1
2. the person eating lime is on the left or right of the person eating cherry##3
3. the person eating lime is on the left or right of the person eating zucchini##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |     2     |  3   |   4    |
| Food   | cherry | lime | zucchini | spinach |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: tea, hot-chocolate, 7up, sprite
1. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
2. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
3. the person drinking 7up is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |   2    |   3   |    4     |
| Beverage   | hot-chocolate | tea | sprite | 7up |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-3::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: photography, chess, writing, sudoku
1. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
2. the person who's hobby is photography is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |    2    |     3      |    4    |
| Hobby   | photography | writing | chess | sudoku |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-4::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: thriller, fantasy, romance, horror
1. the person watching romance movies is on the far right##1
2. the person watching romance movies is on the right of the person watching horror movies##1
3. the person watching thriller movies is on the left or right of the person watching horror movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |  4  |
| Movie-Genre   | fantasy | thriller | horror | romance |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-5::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: badminton, cricket, cycling, rowing
1. the person who's sport is badminton is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person who's sport is cricket is on the right of the person who's sport is cycling##1
3. the person who's sport is badminton is on the right of the person who's sport is cricket##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |    2    |  3   |     4      |
| Sport   | rowing | cycling | cricket | badminton |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-6::.
