3. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left of the person watching disaster movies##1
4. the person watching time-travel movies is on the right of the person watching epic movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |   3   |   4    |
| Movie-Genre   | action | epic | time-travel | disaster |

