.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-10::.
There 4 different types of food: garlic, corn, orange, grapefruit
1. the person eating corn is on the right of the person eating grapefruit##1
2. the person eating corn is between the person eating garlic and the person eating grapefruit##2
3. the person eating garlic is on the left or right of the person eating orange##3
4. the person eating garlic is on the left or right of the person eating orange##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |    2     |    3    |    4    |
| Food   | grapefruit | corn | garlic | orange |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-11::.
4 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, bird, frog, rat
1. the owner of the frog is on the far left##1
2. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left or right of the owner of the bird##3
3. the owner of the bird is on the left or right of the owner of the frog##3

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1    |   2    |     3      |   4    |
| Pet   | frog | bird | guinea-pig | rat |

