.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-20::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: classical, punk, disco, reggae
1. the fan of classical is on the left of the fan of reggae##1
2. the fan of disco is on the left of the fan of punk##1
3. the fan of reggae is on the left or right of the fan of classical##3
4. the fan of punk is on the left of the fan of classical##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1  |  2   |   3   |  4   |
| Music-Genre   | disco | punk | classical | reggae |

 